<title>Hinna Lampi</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Van Belam No Lal Isu chun,
 Hukdamna lampi muh theihna;
 A hun hawngtai, Kalvari ah,
 A nuom taphawtte chieh theihna din.

[V2]
 Ka Hukdmpa ei Tanpa kiengah,
 Ziechun kalvari tang achun;
 Hinna damtui thieng a luong ie,
 Hukdampa nak liem apat chun.

[V3]
 2. Zie hinna damtui khuk achun,
 Damna thisan lun a um hi;
 Gitloh nencheng sawpthien theihna,
 Ei Hukdampa thisan lui luong chu.

[V4]
 3. Hukdampa albang A vaihna,
 Gethsemani huon thim ahi;
 Thing hansedawl chu pu kawmin,
 Kalvari tanglam chu A zuon tai.

[V5]
 4. Kalvari thing kraws chung achun,
 &quot;Ka dang a chak&quot; ti'n A kiko;
 Amah panpih di'n chieh thei leng,
 Hukdampa kawmah Kalvari ah.</lyrics>
</song>